text: Dubensky (; masculine), Dubenskaya (; feminine), or Dubenskoye (; neuter) is the name of several rural localities in Russia: *Dubensky (rural locality), a settlement in Dubensky Settlement Council of Belyayevsky District of Orenburg Oblast *Dubenskoye, Krasnoyarsk Krai, a selo in Sineborsky Selsoviet of Shushensky District of Krasnoyarsk Krai *Dubenskoye, Nizhny Novgorod Oblast, a selo in Dubensky Selsoviet of Vadsky District of Nizhny Novgorod Oblast *Dubenskoye, Penza Oblast, a village in Yermolovsky Selsoviet of Penzensky District of Penza Oblast
title: Dubensky (inhabited locality)
